  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/success\/niai-v-insurance-commissioner\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "NIAI v. Insurance Commissioner" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div id=\"pl-286\" class=\"panel-layout\">\n<div id=\"pg-286-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-286-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pg-286-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_repeat&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;no_margin&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n<div id=\"pgc-286-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-286-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-845 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197.jpg 3061w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197-300x165.jpg 300w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197-768x422.jpg 768w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/IMG_3197-1024x563.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 592px) 100vw, 592px\" \/><\/a>Brought legal action in Jefferson City, Missouri to recover $1,300,000 that belonged to a trust. The funds were in the possession of an insurance company that refused to release funds. I obtained a court order for the release of funds to the client in the sum of $1,300,000.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"pgc-286-1-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-286-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
  "excerpt": {
    "rendered": "<p>Brought legal action in Jefferson City, Missouri to recover $1,300,000 that belonged to a trust. The funds were in the possession of an insurance company that refused to release funds. I obtained a court order for the release of funds to the client in the sum of $1,300,000.<\/p>\n",
    "protected": false
  },
